              <span class="field-content">
               <a href="/advertising-new-curriculum">
                Advertising Is Developing New Curriculum to Prepare Students for Ever-Changing Industry
               </a>
              </span>
             </div>
             <div class="views-field views-field-body">
              <span class="field-content">
               Last year, faculty members in the
               <a href="/degrees/advertising-bs-ms" target="_blank">
                Charles H. Sandage Department of Advertising
               </a>
               voted unanimously not to pursue accreditation from the Accrediting Council on Education in Journalism and Mass Communications, effective Fall 2019. As a result, the department can develop courses more quickly in response to emerging trends in the advertising industry. It also allows the department to create specialized tracks in the major....
