     <div aria-label="Homepage Below Content" class="block block-block" id="block-block-1" role="complementary">
      <h2>
       the college of media at illinois
      </h2>
      <div class="content">
       <p>
        There has never been a more exciting or more important time to study media. The world of media is constantly changing. The public is eager to adopt new technologies.
       </p>
       <p>
        Become a media expert. Learn how to develop content that is informative, strategic, accurate, persuasive, entertaining, creative, targeted and sharable through any media platform.
       </p>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
